dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Hackensack, Bergen Co., New Jersey : including Bogota (Sheet 12)
dct_description_sm: "January 1915." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. "294." Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-26, showing Hackensack; sheets 27-30, showing Bogota, foldered separately. Historic Maps copy imperfect: sheets 13 and 22 wanting.
